Leetcode Question : [The K Weakest Rows in a Matrix](https://leetcode.com/problems/the-k-weakest-rows-in-a-matrix/)

## Approach - 1 (Brute force)

### Java

```java
class Solution {
    public int[] kWeakestRows(int[][] grid, int k) {
        int m = grid.length, n = grid[0].length;
        int[] rowRanks = new int[m];
        int[] result = new int[k];
        
        for(int i = 0; i < m; i++) {
            for(int j = 0; j < n; j++) {
                rowRanks[i] += grid[i][j];
            }
        }

        int l = 0;

        while(k-- > 0) {
            int min = Integer.MAX_VALUE;

            for(int i = 0; i < m; i++) {
                if(min > rowRanks[i]) {
                    result[l] = i;
                    min = rowRanks[i];
                }
            }

            rowRanks[result[l]] = Integer.MAX_VALUE;
            l++;
        }

        return result;
    }
}
```

